quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  27,77,"And it is certainly a guidance and mercy for the believers.",""
  27,78,"Indeed, your Lord will judge between them by His justice, for He is the All-Mighty, the All-Knowing.",""
  27,79,"So put your trust in Allah, for you are upon the clear truth.",""
  27,80,"You cannot make the dead<sup>25</sup> hear, nor can you make the deaf hear the call when they turn their backs retreating.","[25] i.e., whose hearts have died due to their disbelief in Allah."
  27,81,"Nor can you guide the blind out of their error, nor can you make anyone hear except those who believe in Our verses, for they are ready to submit to Allah.",""
  27,82,"When the decree [of the Hour] comes to pass against them, We will bring forth to them a beast<sup>26</sup> out of the earth that will tell them that the people had no faith in Our verses.","[26] The emergence of this beast is one of the major signs of the Day of Judgment; it will speak to people."
  27,83,"And [beware of] the Day when We will gather from every nation a group of those who used to reject Our verses, and they will be driven in ranks.",""
  27,84,"When they finally come, He will say, “Did you reject My verses without even comprehending them, or what exactly were you doing?",""
  27,85,"The decree [of punishment] will befall them because of their wrongdoing, leaving them speechless.",""
  27,86,"Do they not see that We made the night for them to rest in, and made the day bright? Indeed, there are signs in this for people who believe.",""
  27,87,"And [beware of] the Day when the Trumpet will be blown, and all those who are in the heavens and on earth will be horrified except whom Allah wills<sup>27</sup>, and all will come to Him, fully humbled.","[27] The Trumpet will be blown twice: The first blow will cause all to be horrified and then they will die, except whom Allah spares, and the second blow will cause all to be resurrected."
  27,88,"You will see the mountains, thinking them firmly fixed<sup>28</sup>, but they will be moving like clouds – such is the design of Allah, Who has perfected everything. Indeed, He is All-Aware of what you do.","[28] Or solid."
